{"tid":417020,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] Monster Hunter World 2018-01-26","createTime":"2017-09-28T09:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T08:06:54.000Z","uid":67059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3b7563a39a3b6a2c2c402da6d70c952379ada7ce","tid":417020,"uid":67059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到CAPCON個post<br />\n有冇巴絲打會去訂？<br />\n<br />\n======================================<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CAPCOMasia/posts/1681105985241654 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCAPCOMasia%2Fposts%2F1681105985241654%20&d=g497ee0v2v%2FLjIX%2FxLisjW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8d18bdcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CAPCOMasia/posts/1681105985241654 </a><br />\n<br />\nMONSTER HUNTER: WORLD (PS4) 零售版預訂通知：<br />\n<br />\n鑑於近日收到玩家的熱鬧反應，我們在此向大家介紹在香港可以預訂遊戲的店舖及亞洲版MONSTER HUNTER: WORLD的特點：<br />\n<br />\n發售日期：2018年1月26日<br />\n<br />\n- 只有亞洲行版會提供中文介面及字幕，中文介面及字幕將會透過PATCH UPDATE提供。 其他國家(包括日/美/歐版)將不可以下載中文字幕PATCH <br />\n- 亞洲版另提供英/日語音及字幕選擇<br />\n- 亞洲版遊戲可以與全球玩家連線遊玩<br />\n<br />\n光碟版遊戲分為普通版及收藏版，內容分別如下：<br />\n普通版：<br />\n1) 實體包裝遊戲光碟<br />\n2) 初回特典DLC<br />\n<br />\n收藏版：<br />\n1) 實體包裝遊戲光碟 (及初回特典DLC)<br />\n2) Deluxe 版遊戲內容(DLC)，包括：<br />\n- 外觀裝備 「鎧武者系列」<br />\n- 3種追加手勢「正坐」「投射飛鏢」「強推」<br />\n- 2種追加獎章套件「MH歴代角色人物套件」「全熟肉吉祥物套件」<br />\n- 追加塗鴉 「龍」<br />\n- 追加髮型 「沖天炮」<br />\n3) 原裝《滅盡龍》Figure (尺寸: 約W 140mm x D 170mm x H 125mm)<br />\n4) Monster Hunter: World 特別soundtrack CD (10 首)<br />\n5) Monster Hunter: World硬皮畫冊「Monster Designs」(尺寸: W 216mm x H 279mm, 32頁精裝版)<br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://monsterhunterworld.com/hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmonsterhunterworld.com%2Fhk&d=g497ee0v2v%2FLjIX%2FxLisjW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=07f594f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">monsterhunterworld.com/hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另外 仲會出特別版PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n「雄火龍」特別版 PS4 Pro主機 亞洲地區推出詳情待定<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/173237_bb23583b22695a3fc284719b570c81ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F173237_bb23583b22695a3fc284719b570c81ad.jpg&h=97880181&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb1da6e8cdfa4c681c1c63ab28ec06313d27adb8","tid":417020,"uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:23:11.000Z","msg":"我要機啊屌你老母索尼亞洲"},{"pid":"64e1c4e26d243e879b293ddede16ec9462bfa498","tid":417020,"uid":128613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T22:30:23.000Z","msg":"Monster Hunter: World特別版主機 香港有冇得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c065d81bac7ee93f387d6a5cfe8238ead76bf257","tid":417020,"uid":69691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T23:12:16.000Z","msg":"下載版有冇中文字幕？"},{"pid":"bc710c10f3058cd204b40af86069743150d1c9ff","tid":417020,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Monster Hunter: World特別版主機 香港有冇得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n官方未有消息"},{"pid":"e44c57ee0649f8677e0454616f4e33dbd7fe03c7","tid":417020,"uid":9052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下載版有冇中文字幕？</blockquote><br />\n又問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ae692de9a06964bfeee0e3878ed9f3aa22af2d","tid":417020,"uid":128613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20